author: 滇西小哥 Dianxi Xiaoge
description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

Three years ago, we planted a small Monstera cutting at home.
Now it’s bearing clusters of fruits. When ripe, the skin falls off naturally, releasing a fragrance like a blend of pear, apple, and custard apple. The taste is sweet, juicy, and honey-like.
This is my very first time tasting Monstera fruit—what an amazing experience!
三年前在家里种下的一片龟背竹叶，如今长出了满树的果子。
果实成熟后，外皮会自己脱落，香气像梨子、苹果和释迦果的融合，入口甜蜜多汁，像蜂蜜一样。
这是我第一次尝试龟背竹的果实，真的太神奇了！
